2015-07-15 21:47  bernlohr

	* common/fileopen.c (1.20): Input files to fileopen (for reading)
	  can have '.tar.gz' extension, in which case every file in the tar
	  archive is read one after the other (assumed to be not compressed
	  inside the archive).

