	* common/: fileopen.c (1.15), fileopen.h (1.7): Allow general pipes
	  as input or output file names (following '|') if permissive usage
	  of pipes is allowed or the pipe command is in a list of
	  acceptable paths. By default, permissive is off and no paths are
	  pre-defined.

