2014-03-28 16:13  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.102): Add the merge_simtel program to the list of
	  those build by default.

2014-03-28 16:12  bernlohr

	* eventio_basic/: TestIO.cc (1.23), eventio.c (1.36), io_basic.h
	  (1.18), testio.c (1.21): Adding the data length of I/O blocks to
	  the item header, for convenient access also with C functions. The
	  actual length is nevertheless maintained in the I/O buffer and
	  not in the item header. The get_item_begin and the put_item_end
	  calls will copy the actual length to the header.

