2013-04-17 12:32  bernlohr

	* hess/: camera_image.c (1.27), io_hess.c (1.75), read_hess.c
	  (1.98), reconstruct.c (1.50), user_analysis.c (1.58),
	  user_analysis.h (1.26): Implementing first integrator schemes for
	  sample-mode data, which can now be stored as sum data by
	  selecting DST level 0.

2013-04-17 12:29  bernlohr

	* hess/io_hess.h (1.76): Adding two more sub-configurations for
	  CTA_SC: CTA_SC=3 is like CTA_SC=2 now (for prod-2, 11328 pixels,
	  1 gain) but up to 111 telescopes. CTA_SC=4 is what CTA_SC=2 was
	  for HYBRID-1 (11328 pixels but 2 gains).

