	* eventio_basic/EventIO.cc (1.30): Fix g++ 4.5 incompatibility.

2010-08-11 16:10  bernlohr

	* hess/: io_hess.c (1.57), io_hess.h (1.54), read_hess.c (1.79):
	  Get rid of 4095 pixel limitation in raw data. Add sector trigger
	  times to output data.

2010-08-11 16:06  bernlohr

	* eventio_basic/listio.c (1.12): Indentation.

2010-08-06 14:04  bernlohr

	* common/fileopen.c (1.10): Get rid of some of the shells in pipes
	  for compressing/decompressing files on the fly. This may save a
	  bit of main memory. In addition, set errno to EBADMSG if closing
	  a file failed but the underlying fclose/pclose did not set the
	  errno variable.

