	* .cvsignore (1.5): [no log message]

2008-05-24 18:23  bernlohr

	* common/fileopen.c (1.6): Supporting now input from URLs with the
	  help of the curl program.

2008-05-24 16:39  bernlohr

	* hess/: io_hess.c (1.40), read_hess.c (1.56): For DST production
	  in level 2 write neither pulse shape timing nor tracking data of
	  non-triggered telescopes.

2008-05-19 10:40  bernlohr

	* eventio_basic/: EventIO.cc (1.27), EventIO.hh (1.34): Since the
	  C++ interface, in contrast to the C interface, has a properly
	  initialized item version number which we are prepared to handle,
	  we can warn always about a larger than expected version number,
	  even when the item's read function would fail to check
	  explicitly.

