	* eventio_basic/: EventIO.cc (1.23), EventIO.hh (1.29): Add another
	  constructor for easier mixing of C and C++ code.

2007-08-14 16:05  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.69), common/dhsort.c (1.5), common/dhsort.h (1.3),
	  eventio_addon/io_histogram.h (1.7), hess/gen_lookup.c (1.10),
	  hess/io_hess.c (1.29), hess/io_hess.h (1.32), hess/read_hess.c
	  (1.51), hess/rec_tools.c (1.6), hess/rec_tools.h (1.4),
	  hess/reconstruct.c (1.22), hess/reconstruct.h (1.8),
	  hess/user_analysis.c (1.26), hess/user_analysis.h (1.17),
	  root/toroot.cc (1.9): Reverting personal changes by Andre-Claude
	  that he committed by mistake.

2007-08-14 15:41  clapson

	* Makefile (1.68), common/dhsort.c (1.4), common/dhsort.h (1.2),
	  eventio_addon/io_histogram.h (1.6), hess/gen_lookup.c (1.9),
