	* Makefile (1.48): Cannot build a 64-bit version of the hdata2hbook
	  converter on AMD.  There is a CERN library available but only in
	  a 32 bit version.

2005-03-22 11:16  bernlohr

	* doc_src/eventio_de.tex (1.5), doc_src/eventio_en.tex (1.5),
	  eventio_basic/EventIO.cc (1.10), eventio_basic/EventIO.hh (1.15):
	  Add handling of user-defined I/O functions and a couple of other
	  things to the C++ interface.

2005-03-21 17:46  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.47): Force rebuild of generated dependencies also
	  when source files change.

