	* eventio_basic/: EventIO.cc (1.9), EventIO.hh (1.14), io_basic.h
	  (1.7): Integrate user-defined I/O functions into the normal C++
	  interface.

2005-03-21 15:20  bernlohr

	* eventio_addon/io_history.c (1.3): Okay, better make it ISO 8601
	  compliant when changing the date format.

2005-03-21 15:16  bernlohr

	* eventio_addon/io_history.c (1.2): Found some on-Y2K-compliant
	  output in that old code.

2004-07-15 21:46  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.46): Cannot use the C{XX}FLAGS as generated in
	  Makefile.Common here because they mess up the
	  multi-/single-threaded library variants.

2004-07-15 21:04  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.45), common/initial.h (1.6), eventio_basic/EventIO.cc
	  (1.8), eventio_basic/EventIO.hh (1.13), eventio_basic/TestIO.cc
	  (1.9), eventio_basic/eventio.c (1.14), eventio_basic/testio.c
	  (1.10): Porting mainly to AMD 64. Limited success on DEC Unix but
	  who cares.

