	* hess/io_hess.c (1.21): I have to reassign a bit in order to be
	  able to handle a 2048 pixel camera.

2004-06-15 18:14  bernlohr

	* common/hconfig.c (1.9): Even in this old file, valgrind found a
	  variable that, possibly, may be used unitialized.

