	* Makefile (1.42): Also disabling '-O3 -fPIC' here with old
	  binutils although I haven't seen any problems with C code.

2003-10-11 14:51  bernlohr

	* hess/: camera_image.c (1.9), extract_hess.c (1.2): LED events
	  treated and displayed as separate calibration event type.

