	  code.

2003-09-24 12:04  bernlohr

	* eventio_basic/: EventIO.cc (1.4), EventIO.hh (1.7), TestIO.cc
	  (1.4), eventio.c (1.11), io_basic.h (1.5), testio.c (1.6): A new
	  basic data type 'count' was added which is stored with variable
	  length, like in UTF-8 character encoding. This also allows to
	  make C++ interfaces for vectors, valarrays, and string simpler
	  than before.

