	* Makefile (1.26): Now includes Makefile.Common in order to use the
	  same compiler etc. as other modules.

2002-04-17 20:39  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.25), hess/io_hess.h (1.14): Now using larger limits
	  by default, unless HESS_PHASE_1 is defined.

2002-04-17 16:18  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.24), common/hconfig.c (1.4): Cosmetic changes in
	  hconfig configuration listings.

2002-04-17 15:27  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.23), hessio.dox (1.5), corsika/io_simtel.c (1.2),
	  eventio_basic/listio.c (1.4), hess/camera_image.c (1.5),
	  hess/io_hess.c (1.13), hess/io_hess.h (1.13): Several features
	  available via compile-time options are made available by default
	  now. This includes large file (>2 GB) support via the transition
	  method '-D_LARGEFILE64_SOURCE' that should be compatible with
	  ROOT. Also activated by default are now larger limits on the
	  number of pixels and telescopes etc.

