	* hess/io_hess.h (1.12): Allow for more pixels etc. when compiled
	  with -DLARGE_TELESCOPE.

2002-02-26 11:55  bernlohr

	* hess/io_hess.h (1.11): Allow to override numbers of pixels,
	  sectors, drawers to simulate larger cameras.

