	* eventio_basic/testio.c (1.3), hess/io_hess.h (1.10): Fixed typo
	  in text output. Minor changes to documentation.

2001-09-14 14:50  bernlohr

	* hess/: io_hess.c (1.12), io_hess.h (1.9): Replaced 'conv_height'
	  [m] by 'conv_depth' [g/cm^2] because that is the physically
	  relevant variable.

