	* Makefile (1.22): Should be LIBDIR instead of LIBPATH.

2001-08-17 12:47  bernlohr

	* hess/: io_hess.c (1.10), io_hess.h (1.6): Added a few variables
	  that were still missing. New sim_hessarray is required to
	  actually fill them (e.g. maximum of Cherenkov emission).

2001-08-17 12:44  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.21), hessio.dox (1.4): Little modifications in how
	  the documentation is generated.

2001-08-16 18:00  bernlohr

	* eventio_basic/eventio.c (1.5): Fixed a bug each in
	  next_subitem_type and next_subitem_length.  Both functions are
	  only relevant for reading data. Writing was O.K.  While the later
	  function has never been used, the former (next_subitem_type) has
	  lead to NaN in the reconstructed core position.

2001-08-15 19:15  bernlohr

	* hess/: io_hess.c (1.9), io_hess.h (1.5): Minor documentation
	  improvements.  Variable event.shower.img_pattern was missing in
	  the data.

2001-08-14 19:20  bernlohr

	* hess/: io_hess.c (1.8), io_hess.h (1.4): The former 'normal_flag'
	  variable in the run header had never been set. This is fixed now.
	  The variable has also been renamed to make its meaning clearer.
	  Documentation has been made a bit clearer.

2001-08-13 13:23  bernlohr

	* hess/io_hess.c (1.7): The MC event number was not read properly.

