	  <pthread.h> from histogram.c to histogram.h

2001-07-06 15:17  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.20), common/current.c (1.2), common/dhsort.c (1.2),
	  common/hconfig.c (1.3), common/histogram.c (1.2),
