	  (1.2), eventio_basic/listio.c (1.3), hess/camera_image.c (1.4),
	  hess/read_hess.c (1.5): Multithreading issues in histograms and
	  other small changes.

2001-06-28 14:54  bernlohr

	* hess/: camera_image.c (1.3), io_hess.c (1.6): Fixed bug in
	  reading summed raw data with zero-suppression mode 2.

2001-06-27 19:14  bernlohr

	* eventio_basic/: listio.c (1.2), testio.c (1.2): Get rid of minor
	  warnings.

2001-06-18 17:11  bernlohr

	* hess/read_hess.c (1.4): Fixed segmentation fault in case of
	  missing arguments.

2001-06-18 11:34  bernlohr

	* hess/io_hess.c (1.5): Use zero_suppression=3 now for automatic
	  determination of optimum mode.

2001-06-18 11:06  bernlohr

	* hess/: camera_image.c (1.2), io_hess.c (1.4), io_hess.h (1.3):
	  Fixed bug with raw data using zero-suppression or data reduction,
	  where low-gain and high-gain channels were mixed up.

2001-06-08 13:00  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.19), hbook/tohbook.h (1.2): More fine-tuning in
	  Makefile.

2001-06-07 23:00  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.18): Replace some '$(wildcard ...' with '$(shell ls
	  ...' because $(wildcard is evaluated immidately on Mandrake 8.0.

2001-06-07 22:23  bernlohr

	* Makefile (1.17): Warning about 'traditional' things are too
	  boring with gcc 2.96.

